<div class="nbunit" id="25Apr1934"><font color="red">25 April 1934</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Frank Budgen): I&apos;ve just come here to Paris &hellip; I saw Vogt in Z&apos;ch &hellip; upset by the tragic death [March 1934] of my friend Borach &hellip; I prefer Puffing Billy [train] to Staggering Bob [automobile] </div>
